  notes:
    - "This spec covers: threading.TIMEOUT_MAX.__class__.__name__ 'float', __gt__(0) True; type(threading._main_thread).__name__ '_MainThread', __module__ 'threading'; threading.excepthook.__class__.__name__ 'builtin_function_or_method', __module__ '_thread'; threading.ExceptHookArgs.__name__ '_ExceptHookArgs', __module__ '_thread'; threading.__spec__.name 'threading', __class__.__name__ 'ModuleSpec' (Wave 281)."
    - "threading.TIMEOUT_MAX.__class__.__name__ == 'float' — TIMEOUT_MAX is a float constant (approximately sys.maxsize as float) imported from _thread; __class__.__name__ is 'float'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "threading.TIMEOUT_MAX.__gt__(0) == True — TIMEOUT_MAX is a large positive float (9223372036.0 on 64-bit systems). Verified with Python 3.14.3."
